Package cellularAutomata.help

Class Summary
BrowserLoader Opens Internet Explorer to display help pages.
CAGettingStarted Creates a "getting started" browser for newbies.
CAGuidedTour Opens a "Guided Tour" browser page for newbies.
CAHelp Creates a help browser.
CAHowManyRulesAreThere Opens a browser with the a URL containing info on how many rules are in the CA Explorer.
CAHowToWriteYourOwnRule Opens a browser with the a URL containing info on writing your own rule.
CAIncreasingMemoryTutorial Opens a tutorial (browser page) for increasing memory and speed.
CAObesityTutorial Opens a "Obesity Tutorial" browser page for obesity researchers.
CAPropertiesChanged Opens a browser with a URL containing info on how the properties object has changed in the CA Explorer.
CARuleConstructors Opens a browser with a URL containing info on how to build constructors for rules in the CA Explorer.
CAShowHiddenTabs Opens a browser with the a URL containing info on how to display hidden tabs (in other words, how to press the All button).
